Aah!

593
00:44:06,543 --> 00:44:08,750
BUGSPRAY:
This way!

594
00:44:09,647 --> 00:44:11,649
[♪♪♪]

595
00:44:21,358 --> 00:44:22,928
[BEEPING]

596
00:44:25,629 --> 00:44:27,131
[HERO GASPS]

597
00:44:33,570 --> 00:44:35,505
Get to the airlock.

598
00:44:35,506 --> 00:44:37,452
[♪♪♪]

599
00:44:39,510 --> 00:44:43,117
Bridge, we're heading to the airlock.
And they are right on our ass.

600
00:44:43,280 --> 00:44:45,021
DAUGHERTY:
Roger that.

601
00:44:45,649 --> 00:44:46,684
HERO:
Goddamn it.

602
00:44:52,523 --> 00:44:54,196
[MAN 1 GROANS AND SCREAMS]

