00:45:37,668 --> 00:45:39,477
RATZASS:
Chow!

608
00:45:39,636 --> 00:45:41,206
Run!

609
00:45:41,505 --> 00:45:44,384
IBANEZ:
Alesia, we are under
massive bug attack!

