It's jammed!

619
00:46:36,794 --> 00:46:38,796
[GROANING]

620
00:46:40,731 --> 00:46:45,111
Don't suppose you have a good
replacement pan to fix this.

621
00:46:45,269 --> 00:46:46,577
[GRUNTING]

622
00:46:47,371 --> 00:46:49,044
You're gonna make it.

623
00:46:49,206 --> 00:46:50,913
Oh, that's right.

624
00:46:51,074 --> 00:46:56,547
You can't let me die.
I'm the only one of
your patients that's lived.

625
00:47:05,522 --> 00:47:07,524
[♪♪♪]

626
00:47:14,097 --> 00:47:16,236
HERO:
Open the air lock.

627
00:47:19,069 --> 00:47:22,482
Shock Jock, you go first.
SHOCK JOCK: Yes, sir.

628
00:47:29,913 --> 00:47:31,950
What the hell? Evasive action.

629
00:47:37,621 --> 00:47:38,998
ICE BLONDE:
Shock Jock!

630
00:47:39,189 --> 00:47:41,191
[♪♪♪]

631
00:47:49,466 --> 00:47:51,275
DAUGHERTY:
What the hell just happened?

632
00:47:51,435 --> 00:47:52,846
The Alesia's gone.

633
00:47:53,003 --> 00:47:58,077
Did we just fire on them?
Alesia, Captain Jonah, answer me.

