00:48:04,314 --> 00:48:07,989
Listen up, everybody.
We head to the bridge now.

636
00:48:09,820 --> 00:48:14,200
Since when is she giving the orders?
Since we boarded her ship.

637
00:48:14,358 --> 00:48:15,666
Just asking.

638
00:48:15,826 --> 00:48:16,827
[BUGS SCREECHING]

639
00:48:16,994 --> 00:48:18,735
Bugs!

640
00:48:18,896 --> 00:48:20,898
[♪♪♪]

641
00:48:28,005 --> 00:48:29,916
JENKINS [ON MONITOR]:
I hacked her, so she hacked me.

