00:48:52,062 --> 00:48:53,097
IBANEZ:
You know,

646
00:48:53,263 --> 00:48:55,573
if I wanted to run this much,

647
00:48:55,732 --> 00:48:58,679
I would have joined
the mobile infantry.

648
00:49:01,872 --> 00:49:04,716
Captain Ibanez to the L-6 Base.

649
00:49:04,875 --> 00:49:08,448
High command,
this is the John A. Warden.

650
00:49:08,645 --> 00:49:11,251
Johnny, please respond.

651
00:49:11,415 --> 00:49:14,225
Communication is always jaggy
near wormholes.

652
00:49:14,384 --> 00:49:17,524
Recommend we position ourselves
away from the nebula.

653
00:49:17,688 --> 00:49:22,103
How did the cannons fire?
And why target our own ship?

654
00:49:22,259 --> 00:49:24,432
Jenkins tried to warn us.

655
00:49:24,594 --> 00:49:26,574
Carl is alive?

656
00:49:26,763 --> 00:49:30,643
Locked himself in a bug cage.
And you're just now telling me this?

657
00:49:30,801 --> 00:49:35,250
Look, captain, if you're ready
for a full debriefing, I'm all for it.

658
00:49:35,906 --> 00:49:37,044
Hero.

659
00:49:37,207 --> 00:49:42,054
Jenkins found a queen on Fort Casey.
He ordered us to capture it alive.

660
00:49:43,046 --> 00:49:44,116
What the--?

661
00:49:44,281 --> 00:49:45,783
Tell her the rest, major.

662
00:49:45,949 --> 00:49:49,123
IBANEZ:
Yes, major. Tell me the rest of it.

663
00:49:49,286 --> 00:49:53,063
I knew trying to take the queen
would result in heavy casualties.

664
00:49:53,223 --> 00:49:56,636
I wasn't gonna sacrifice my men
for a bug hunt.

665
00:49:56,793 --> 00:49:59,467
So that's why
he had you arrested.

666
00:50:00,430 --> 00:50:02,706
But he got the queen
after all.

667
00:50:03,233 --> 00:50:07,739
Wait a minute. How the hell
can a bug control a starship?

668
00:50:07,904 --> 00:50:09,941
HERO:
You're gonna have to ask
Jenkins that.

669
00:50:11,208 --> 00:50:12,482
MAN:
What the--?

670
00:50:17,080 --> 00:50:19,082
[♪♪♪]

671
00:50:31,595 --> 00:50:32,630
We're moving.

672
00:50:32,796 --> 00:50:34,104
