straight to Earth.

685
00:51:33,557 --> 00:51:36,766
This is Captain Ibanez
to the L-6 Base.

686
00:51:36,927 --> 00:51:39,601
Captain Ibanez calling L-6 Base.

687
00:51:40,230 --> 00:51:42,733
This is Captain Ibanez
to Johnny Rico.

688
00:51:42,899 --> 00:51:46,813
L-6 Base come in.
This is Captain lb--

689
00:51:51,408 --> 00:51:53,820
What the hell
are you doing?

690
00:52:02,018 --> 00:52:06,262
If she is in the engine room,
then I'm gonna hunt her down.

691
00:52:06,423 --> 00:52:07,731
I'll back you up.

692
00:52:07,891 --> 00:52:11,361
No. You stay.

693
00:52:11,528 --> 00:52:15,271
Besides, you'll never be able
to fit through here.

694
00:52:16,600 --> 00:52:18,409
I'll be back.

695
00:52:29,579 --> 00:52:31,616
You're not gonna stop her?

696
00:52:31,781 --> 00:52:34,387
ICE BLONDE:
She's a big girl.
