00:55:33,029 --> 00:55:34,804
[GUNFIRE]

728
00:55:34,964 --> 00:55:36,807
[MEN YELLING]

729
00:55:43,606 --> 00:55:45,051
[BUG WHIMPERS]

730
00:55:46,142 --> 00:55:47,280
Aah!

731
00:55:49,346 --> 00:55:53,419
The L-6 Base.
We've got to warn Johnny.

732
00:55:56,920 --> 00:55:58,957
Morse code.
We can't use the beacon.

733
00:55:59,122 --> 00:56:03,161
