739
00:56:29,219 --> 00:56:31,722
It's Morse code.

740
00:56:32,288 --> 00:56:35,030
They're trying to send us
a message.

741
00:56:36,659 --> 00:56:39,105
Repeat. Bugs in control.

742
00:56:43,133 --> 00:56:46,546
How the hell do bugs
control a starship?

743
00:56:49,706 --> 00:56:52,653
