Deployment status?

745
00:56:56,646 --> 00:57:00,423
WOMAN:
Sheridan, Ishizuka, and the Franklin
are heading to intercept.

746
00:57:04,687 --> 00:57:06,689
[♪♪♪]

747
00:57:14,697 --> 00:57:16,699
[SHRIEKS]

748
00:57:33,216 --> 00:57:36,390
WOMAN:
The Sheridan has taken
catastrophic damage.

749
00:57:52,435 --> 00:57:55,109
The Franklin is critical
but operational.

750
00:57:55,271 --> 00:57:59,378
Franklin, disengage.
Get clear of the John A. Warden.

751
00:58:00,743 --> 00:58:02,745
[♪♪♪]

752
00:58:07,050 --> 00:58:09,052
[ALL GRUNT]

753
00:58:16,593 --> 00:58:20,234
WOMAN:
The John A. Warden's approaching,
on a crash course.

754
00:58:20,396 --> 00:58:24,640
Ready to intercept, sir.
Main cannon armed and ready.

755
00:58:24,801 --> 00:58:26,644
Carmen...

756
00:58:26,803 --> 00:58:28,646
[ALARM WAILING]

757
00:58:28,805 --> 00:58:30,182
Carl...

758
00:58:30,340 --> 00:58:31,910
Commander!

759
00:58:36,079 --> 00:58:37,922
Open...

760
00:58:40,216 --> 00:58:41,422
fire!

761
00:58:42,485 --> 00:58:44,487
[♪♪♪]

762
00:58:49,125 --> 00:58:50,126
Fire!

763
00:58:50,293 --> 00:58:54,002
Sir. We can't fire now.
They're too close.

764
00:58:55,865 --> 00:58:57,970
[♪♪♪]

765
00:59:12,315 --> 00:59:17,287
They missed us, sir.
Yeah. But why?

766
00:59:17,820 --> 00:59:19,857
Commander,
I have the Warden's trajectory.

767
00:59:20,023 --> 00:59:22,367
It's heading straight for the Earth.

768
00:59:22,992 --> 00:59:26,701
RICO:
They never meant to ram us.
We were just in their way.

769
00:59:31,768 --> 00:59:34,248
RICO:
This is General Rico
to Earth Defense Command.

770
00:59:34,404 --> 00:59:36,577
The John A. Warden
is under bug control

771
00:59:36,773 --> 00:59:38,411
and entering Earth's atmosphere.

772
00:59:38,575 --> 00:59:41,988
It's what? The John A. Warden?

773
00:59:42,278 --> 00:59:46,021
Rico, I don't care if John A. Warden
is on that ship himself,

774
00:59:46,182 --> 00:59:48,890
if that ship is infested,
you take it down.

775
00:59:49,052 --> 00:59:54,092
Just give me a chance to do both, sir.
Rescue our men and gain control.

776
00:59:54,290 --> 00:59:57,066
Rico...
Commander, I promise.

777
00:59:57,226 --> 01:00:01,174
A bug invasion will not happen
on my watch, sir.

778
01:00:01,331 --> 01:00:02,935
It better not.

779
01:00:04,601 --> 01:00:07,548
Spaceborne command.
Prepare a drop.

780
01:00:08,338 --> 01:00:10,340
[♪♪♪]

781
01:00:14,944 --> 01:00:16,617
BUGSPRAY:
What now?

782
01:00:16,813 --> 01:00:20,420
Daugherty, you stay here
and protect the captain.

783
01:00:21,317 --> 01:00:24,628
The rest of you, lock and load.

784
01:00:24,821 --> 01:00:27,563
It's time we exterminate that bitch.

785
01:00:29,025 --> 01:00:30,595
ALL:
Hoo-ah!

786
01:00:30,760 --> 01:00:32,762
[♪♪♪]

787
01:00:40,403 --> 01:00:41,473
[GASPS]

788
01:00:42,538 --> 01:00:45,485
IBANEZ:
She's trying to crash the ship.

789
01:00:49,212 --> 01:00:51,249
DAUGHERTY:
Do what you have to do!

790
01:01:04,560 --> 01:01:06,870
I don't know what to do.

791
01:01:12,735 --> 01:01:14,976
Trig, where are you now?

792
01:01:15,772 --> 01:01:18,184
Trig, location?

793
01:01:18,975 --> 01:01:21,012
Trig, come in.

794
01:01:21,177 --> 01:01:23,179
Trig, respond.

795
01:01:23,379 --> 01:01:25,154
Where are you? Trig!

796
01:01:25,314 --> 01:01:26,793
TRIG [OVER RADIO]:
Central storage area.

797
01:01:26,949 --> 01:01:28,758
Have you found the queen?

798
01:01:28,918 --> 01:01:32,331
TRIG:
Oh, yeah. This bitch is disgusting.

799
01:01:32,822 --> 01:01:35,598
Take her out.
Done.

800
01:01:35,758 --> 01:01:37,294
IBANEZ:
We're running out of time.

801
01:01:37,460 --> 01:01:39,201
Do you read me?

802
01:01:39,395 --> 01:01:41,102
Loud and clear, captain.

803
01:01:41,264 --> 01:01:42,902
[♪♪♪]

804
01:01:48,404 --> 01:01:50,645
[SHRIEKING]

805
01:01:52,275 --> 01:01:53,686
Shit.

806
01:01:53,843 --> 01:01:55,652
In that case...

807
01:02:01,684 --> 01:02:03,686
[♪♪♪]

808
01:02:10,059 --> 01:02:12,061
[ALARM WAILING]

809
01:02:13,429 --> 01:02:14,874
That's it.

810
01:02:15,498 --> 01:02:17,136
[♪♪♪]

811
01:02:30,079 --> 01:02:31,149
[ALARM WAILING]

812
01:02:32,448 --> 01:02:34,155
[GRUNTS]

813
01:02:39,756 --> 01:02:40,928
[GASPS]

814
01:02:41,090 --> 01:02:42,330
[BUGS SCREECHING]

815
01:02:42,558 --> 01:02:44,401
[GRUNTING]

816
01:02:51,467 --> 01:02:52,775
[BUGS SCREECHING]

817
01:02:53,002 --> 01:02:54,037
Oh, shit.

818
01:02:54,203 --> 01:02:57,844
Four-thirty-eight, 439.

819
01:02:58,474 --> 01:03:00,545
Four-forty...

820
01:03:02,979 --> 01:03:04,185
[TRIG SCREAMS]

821
01:03:04,347 --> 01:03:05,758
Trig...

822
01:03:05,915 --> 01:03:08,623
All hands, prepare for impact.

823
01:03:08,918 --> 01:03:10,920
[♪♪♪]

824
01:03:11,921 --> 01:03:14,765
HERO:
Magnetic stabilizers on.

825
01:03:21,230 --> 01:03:23,232
[GRUNTING]

826
01:03:23,933 --> 01:03:25,571
[ALL GRUNTING]

827
01:03:42,318 --> 01:03:44,924
[SHIP BEEPING]

828
01:04:09,245 --> 01:04:12,590
All hands, report.

829
01:04:13,616 --> 01:04:15,926
Can anybody hear me?

830
01:04:16,986 --> 01:04:18,556
Hero.

831
01:04:19,055 --> 01:04:20,762
Anybody?

832
01:04:21,858 --> 01:04:23,860
[CLICKING AND CLATTERING]

833
01:04:29,765 --> 01:04:31,506
Lieutenant.

834
01:04:48,951 --> 01:04:50,218
Thank you.

835
01:05:01,864 --> 01:05:03,866
[♪♪♪]

836
01:05:06,102 --> 01:05:08,378
COMMANDER:
Rico, you're not a trooper anymore.

837
01:05:08,537 --> 01:05:09,880
Remember that.

838
01:05:10,673 --> 01:05:12,812
RICO:
I'm always a trooper.

839
01:05:12,975 --> 01:05:16,548
And if there are any of our men alive
on that ship,

840
01:05:17,113 --> 01:05:19,354
I'm getting them out.

841
01:05:19,682 --> 01:05:21,559
COMMANDER:
Should've known you'd say that.

842
01:05:21,984 --> 01:05:24,021
Kill them any way you can.

843
01:05:24,186 --> 01:05:25,824
Kill them all.

844
01:05:27,156 --> 01:05:31,662
In T-minus 30, we'll send nukes
to sanitize that site.

845
01:05:31,827 --> 01:05:34,831
So be out of there before we hit.

846
01:05:35,431 --> 01:05:36,671
Don't wait for me.

847
01:05:36,832 --> 01:05:40,211
If I'm not out in 30, nuke it.

848
01:05:41,337 --> 01:05:43,339
[♪♪♪]

849
01:05:45,207 --> 01:05:47,209
[BUGS SCREECHING]

850
01:05:55,384 --> 01:05:57,159
HOLYMAN:
Ice! Unh!

851
01:05:58,788 --> 01:06:00,165
[MEN GRUNTING]

852
01:06:00,356 --> 01:06:01,664
Holyman!

853
01:06:02,558 --> 01:06:05,539
BUGSPRAY:
What the hell kind of bug is that?

854
01:06:09,031 --> 01:06:10,169
Fuck me!

855
01:06:11,033 --> 01:06:13,035
[GROANING]

856
01:06:16,706 --> 01:06:18,379
[SIGHS]

857
01:06:18,574 --> 01:06:22,283
I was just starting to believe you.
HERO: Fall back now!

858
01:06:29,285 --> 01:06:31,322
[♪♪♪]

859
01:06:31,487 --> 01:06:32,989
RICO:
Troopers.

860
01:06:33,189 --> 01:06:36,398
Our mission is to storm the wreck
of the John A. Warden,

861
01:06:36,559 --> 01:06:38,300
rescue our surviving men

862
01:06:39,462 --> 01:06:43,239
and kill every last
son-of-a-bitch bug we see.

863
01:06:43,399 --> 01:06:45,504
Do you understand?
ALL [OVER RADIO]: Yes, sir!

864
01:06:45,701 --> 01:06:49,308
We've got 25 minutes
before they level that site.

865
01:06:49,472 --> 01:06:52,976
So move fast. And remember.

866
01:06:53,142 --> 01:06:56,589
We're not fighting for some rock
across the galaxy.

867
01:06:56,746 --> 01:06:58,282
We're fighting for our home!

868
01:06:59,281 --> 01:07:00,521
Commence the attack.

869
01:07:11,127 --> 01:07:12,800
[WARBLING AND RUMBLING]

870
01:07:12,962 --> 01:07:14,134
[GRUNTS]

871
01:07:14,363 --> 01:07:15,535
[♪♪♪]

872
01:07:15,731 --> 01:07:17,733
[CHITTERING]

873
01:07:22,972 --> 01:07:26,146
MAN [WHISPERS]: Over here.
This way.

874
01:07:32,815 --> 01:07:34,658
[GRUNTS]

875
01:07:39,789 --> 01:07:41,393
[GUNFIRE]

876
01:07:50,900 --> 01:07:53,312
Are you all right, captain?
IBANEZ: Yeah.

877
01:07:53,469 --> 01:07:55,676
Thanks.
Come on.

878
01:07:55,838 --> 01:07:58,876
Let's get to the air lock
and get out of here.

879
01:08:02,044 --> 01:08:04,320
That voice...

880
01:08:04,580 --> 01:08:06,582
[♪♪♪]

881
01:08:12,922 --> 01:08:15,835
Purging now!

882
01:08:16,692 --> 01:08:18,694
[♪♪♪]

883
01:08:24,900 --> 01:08:28,040
Come on, you apes.
You wanna live forever?

884
01:08:28,938 --> 01:08:30,918
Kill them all!

885
01:08:42,585 --> 01:08:44,587
[BUZZER SOUNDING]

886
01:08:47,123 --> 01:08:49,535
She still has the ship.

887
01:08:53,762 --> 01:08:55,969
Ice, you guard the captain.

888
01:08:56,132 --> 01:08:58,203
The rest of you
are coming with me.

889
01:08:58,367 --> 01:09:01,371
We're gonna kill the queen
and take back the ship.

890
01:09:01,537 --> 01:09:03,141
Good luck.

891
01:09:08,544 --> 01:09:11,753
Don't worry.
You'll see your kids soon.

892
01:09:11,914 --> 01:09:16,226
But those bugs?
We're taking their mama down.

893
01:09:21,790 --> 01:09:24,066
MAN 1: Holy shit!
MAN 2: Take evasive action!

894
01:09:24,226 --> 01:09:26,832
MAN 3:
Incoming. Run and gun!

895
01:09:26,996 --> 01:09:28,805
[MAN 4 SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY]

896
01:09:30,099 --> 01:09:31,942
[FOOTSTEPS]

897
01:09:33,302 --> 01:09:35,248
[ENGINE HUMMING]

898
01:09:35,671 --> 01:09:37,378
HERO:
Listen.

899
01:09:38,073 --> 01:09:39,746
BUGSPRAY:
It's the engine.

900
01:09:39,909 --> 01:09:42,480
Mech, still have explosives?

901
01:09:42,645 --> 01:09:44,625
MECH:
Some C4.

902
01:09:49,451 --> 01:09:51,453
[BUGS SCREECHING]

903
01:10:04,934 --> 01:10:06,936
[♪♪♪]

904
01:10:13,342 --> 01:10:15,015
BUGSPRAY:
Trig. No.

905
01:10:15,177 --> 01:10:16,520
[♪♪♪]

906
01:10:17,913 --> 01:10:19,620
Trig.

907
01:10:20,282 --> 01:10:22,023
Trig!

908
01:10:24,119 --> 01:10:25,621
No.

909
01:10:27,523 --> 01:10:29,469
[BUG SCREECHING]

910
01:10:29,692 --> 01:10:31,433
[GRUNTING]

911
01:10:35,030 --> 01:10:36,873
Ambush.

912
01:10:45,708 --> 01:10:48,848
Go, sir. I'll hold them off
for as long as I can.

913
01:10:51,680 --> 01:10:53,751
Four-forty-one,

914
01:10:53,949 --> 01:10:58,056
442, 443,

915
01:10:58,220 --> 01:11:00,700
444.

916
01:11:02,191 --> 01:11:04,193
[♪♪♪]

917
01:11:07,329 --> 01:11:09,331
[BUGS SCREECHING]

918
01:11:35,257 --> 01:11:36,759
Damn.

919
01:11:39,728 --> 01:11:41,799
What the hell?

920
01:11:45,034 --> 01:11:47,913
This is what
I've been working on.

921
01:11:50,773 --> 01:11:53,049
MAN [OVER RADIO]:
T-minus 60 till launch.

922
01:11:53,208 --> 01:11:54,881
Starting ﬁnal countdown.

923
01:11:55,044 --> 01:11:57,718
Fifty-six, 55,

924
01:11:57,880 --> 01:12:00,656
54, 53,

925
01:12:00,816 --> 01:12:04,161
52, 51...

926
01:12:04,320 --> 01:12:06,322
[BUGS SCREECHING]

927
01:12:12,895 --> 01:12:15,136
RICO:
Carmen, get down!

928
01:12:28,811 --> 01:12:30,813
[♪♪♪]

929
01:12:37,052 --> 01:12:38,827
Johnny?

930
01:12:39,922 --> 01:12:42,266
Are there any other survivors?
ICE BLONDE: Four more.

931
01:12:42,424 --> 01:12:44,199
Heading to kill the queen.

932
01:12:44,360 --> 01:12:45,964
And...

933
01:12:46,595 --> 01:12:47,835
Jenkins?

934
01:12:47,996 --> 01:12:50,636
You're still alive?
I can't die yet.

935
01:12:51,133 --> 01:12:53,135
Not until we win this war at least.

936
01:12:54,002 --> 01:12:56,448
So, by controlling
the bugs, you...

937
01:12:56,605 --> 01:12:59,950
I can bring us one step closer
to winning the war.

938
01:13:00,109 --> 01:13:04,182
And I can get you close enough
to kill the queen.

939
01:13:07,950 --> 01:13:10,157
Then let's get moving.

940
01:13:13,789 --> 01:13:15,791
[♪♪♪]

941
01:13:30,406 --> 01:13:34,650
QUEEN [AS DAUGHERTY]:
Let's negotiate.

942
01:13:35,377 --> 01:13:37,220
HERO:
Daugherty?

943
01:13:42,684 --> 01:13:45,665
Surrender Jenkins to us

944
01:13:45,821 --> 01:13:49,166
and we will let you live.

945
01:13:49,324 --> 01:13:51,201
They fear me.

946
01:13:51,360 --> 01:13:53,863
Maybe they just think
you're an asshole.

947
01:13:54,563 --> 01:13:56,042
Fuck off.

948
01:13:56,198 --> 01:13:58,405
Then, you die!

949
01:13:58,734 --> 01:14:00,736
[♪♪♪]

950
01:14:03,405 --> 01:14:04,679
[BUGS SCREECHING]

951
01:14:16,251 --> 01:14:19,095
These are the last ones
I can control directly for now.

952
01:14:19,254 --> 01:14:22,758
If I could have finished my research--
HERO: Then finish it.

953
01:14:22,925 --> 01:14:25,531
So we can end this.

954
01:14:25,694 --> 01:14:27,696
Run.
What?

955
01:14:27,863 --> 01:14:31,072
I said run!

956
01:14:39,408 --> 01:14:40,443
MAN [OVER RADIO]:
Three.

957
01:14:40,609 --> 01:14:42,088
Two. One.

958
01:14:42,244 --> 01:14:44,224
Launch.

959
01:14:49,918 --> 01:14:54,458
BUGSPRAY:
Four-fifty-four, 455,

960
01:14:54,623 --> 01:14:59,072
456, 457,

961
01:14:59,228 --> 01:15:01,265
458...

962
01:15:12,574 --> 01:15:13,644
RICO:
Carl!

963
01:15:23,318 --> 01:15:25,320
[♪♪♪]

964
01:15:27,923 --> 01:15:29,630
JENKINS:
Johnny Rico.

965
01:15:29,791 --> 01:15:32,829
I should leave your ass here
to get nuked.

966
01:15:33,462 --> 01:15:36,170
What do you mean "nuked"?
Let's go.

967
01:15:40,602 --> 01:15:42,604
[♪♪♪]

968
01:15:46,775 --> 01:15:49,517
IBANEZ:
Johnny, the landing ship is here.

969
01:15:50,846 --> 01:15:52,189
I'm coming.

970
01:16:05,060 --> 01:16:07,062
[♪♪♪]

971
01:16:09,965 --> 01:16:12,036
WOMAN [OVER RADIO]:
We lost contact
with the landing ship.

972
01:16:12,200 --> 01:16:14,840
MAN:
T-minus-15 until impact.

973
01:16:16,305 --> 01:16:17,909
[BEEPING]

974
01:16:24,146 --> 01:16:25,284
Where's the ship?

975
01:16:33,589 --> 01:16:35,034
No.

976
01:16:41,363 --> 01:16:43,365
[♪♪♪]

977
01:16:49,171 --> 01:16:51,549
They took out the nuke.

978
01:16:52,240 --> 01:16:54,242
[SHRIEKS]

979
01:16:55,210 --> 01:16:57,212
[BUGS SCREECHING]

980
01:17:05,921 --> 01:17:07,901
She's won.

981
01:17:08,757 --> 01:17:10,031
I still have one.

982
01:17:10,926 --> 01:17:12,234
One what?

983
01:17:12,894 --> 01:17:15,465
The shuttle I used to evacuate
from Fort Casey.

984
01:17:16,064 --> 01:17:19,637
Heh. Then let's use it.
She'll never let us leave.

985
01:17:19,835 --> 01:17:20,939
[GUNFIRE]

986
01:17:21,103 --> 01:17:23,105
[MEN YELLING]

987
01:17:23,972 --> 01:17:25,713
ICE BLONDE:
You son of a bitch.

988
01:17:25,874 --> 01:17:28,980
RATZASS:
Aw. Now that's not nice.

989
01:17:29,144 --> 01:17:31,556
Tell them.
I set explosives on the main engine.

990
01:17:32,080 --> 01:17:33,582
What?

991
01:17:34,983 --> 01:17:37,224
HERO [IN VOICE-OVER]:
Mech, still have explosives?

992
01:17:37,386 --> 01:17:41,232
MECH: Some C4.
HERO: Good.

993
01:17:41,390 --> 01:17:43,893
If we put the C4
in the main engine,

994
01:17:44,059 --> 01:17:47,268
we can blow up the ship
and the queen with it.

995
01:17:47,629 --> 01:17:49,609
Whoa.

996
01:17:50,265 --> 01:17:52,609
We might not make it out
in time.

997
01:17:54,369 --> 01:17:56,246
At least they won't.

998
01:17:56,405 --> 01:17:57,679
[SIGHS]

999
01:17:58,507 --> 01:17:59,611
Okay.

1000
01:18:00,108 --> 01:18:01,951
Then do it.

1001
01:18:02,110 --> 01:18:06,422
Ratzass, watch his back.
RATZASS: Yes, sir.

1002
01:18:09,251 --> 01:18:11,697
RATZASS:
So the extraction team's
been wiped out?

1003
01:18:13,021 --> 01:18:15,189
Just 10 minutes left.

1004
01:18:16,324 --> 01:18:18,133
[♪♪♪]

1005
01:18:18,427 --> 01:18:20,703
Johnny, what are you doing?

1006
01:18:22,464 --> 01:18:23,807
Get to the shuttle.

1007
01:18:26,301 --> 01:18:27,837
Johnny!

1008
01:18:29,104 --> 01:18:30,777
