the three of us are working together.

1063
01:23:51,926 --> 01:23:53,599
Are we, Carl?

1064
01:23:53,762 --> 01:23:58,040
Pardon?
Are we? Working together?

1065
01:23:59,334 --> 01:24:01,439
Cheer up, Johnny.
You're a hero.

1066
01:24:01,603 --> 01:24:03,014
